Pivovarna Lasko (PILR)  Group d.d. of
Slovenia received an offer for commercial cooperation from
Konzum d.d., the Croatian retail chain owned by Agrokor d.d.,
STA newswire  reported , citing the Slovenian company.  Agrokor on March 10 made a bid for a 23.3 percent of
 Mercator Poslovni Sistem (MELR)  d.d., which is being sold by Pivovarna
Lasko.  To contact the reporter on this story:
